\c 5
\nb
\v 1 Umphefumulo, uba usona-ke usuzwe ilizwi lesifungo\x + 1 Kho. 8.31. Mat. 26.63.\x*, njalo ube ngumfakazi, kumbe ukubonile loba ukwazi, uba ungakukhulumi, uzathwala ububi bawo\x + 5. 17; 7.18; 10.17; 17.16; 19.8; 20.17,19. Nani 5.31; 20.20; 9.13.\x*.
\v 2 Loba uba umphefumulo uthinta loba yiyiphi into engcolileyo\x + 11.24,28,31,39. Nani 19.11,13,16.\x*, loba iyisidumbu senyamazana engcolileyo, loba isidumbu sesifuyo esingcolileyo, kumbe isidumbu salokho okuhuquzelayo okungcolileyo, lanxa kufihliwe kuye, kube kanti ungcolile ulecala\x + 5.17.\x*.
\v 3 Loba uba uthinta ukungcola komuntu\x + 12.1,2; 13.1,2; 15.1,2.\x*, loba kuyini ukungcola kwakhe angcola ngakho, njalo kufihliwe kuwo, lapho usukwazi uzakuba lecala.
\v 4 Loba uba umphefumulo ufunga, ukhuluma ngamawala ngendebe zawo\x + Hlab. 106.33; Nani 30.6,8; Zaga 12.18.\x* ukwenza okubi loba ukwenza okuhle\x + 1 Sam. 25.22. Mark. 6.23. Seb. 23.12.\x*, loba kuyini umuntu angakhuluma ngakho ngamawala ngesifungo, njalo kufihliwe kuwo, lapho usukwazi uzakuba lecala kokunye kwalokho.
\v 5 Kuzakuthi-ke nxa ulecala kwenye yalezizinto, uvume ngalokho okonileyo\x + 16.21; 26.40; Nani 5.7; Ezra 10.1; Josh. 7.19.\x*,
\v 6 ulethe umnikelo wawo wecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngesono sawo osonileyo, ensikazi emhlanjini, iwundlu loba izinyane lembuzi, kube ngumnikelo wesono, umpristi abesewenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ngesono sawo.
\v 7 Kodwa uba isandla sawo singafinyeleli okwanela imvu, ungaletha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngecala lawo olonileyo amajuba amabili\x + 1.14.\x* loba amaphuphu enkwilimba amabili, elinye libe ngumnikelo wesono lelinye libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa;
\v 8 ubusuwaletha kumpristi ozanikela elingelomnikelo wesono kuqala, atshuphule inhloko yalo entanyeni yalo, kodwa angakwehlukanisi\x + 1.15,17.\x*,
\v 9 afafaze okwegazi lomnikelo wesono ehlangothini lwelathi, legazi eliseleyo likhanyelwe\x + 1.15.\x* kungaphansi yelathi\x + 4.7,18,30,34.\x*; kungumnikelo wesono.
\v 10 Elesibili uzalenza libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa njengokwesimiso, lompristi amenzele inhlawulo yokuthula ngesono sakhe asonileyo\x + 4.20,26,31,35; 4.13,16.\x*, njalo uzathethelelwa.
\p
\v 11 Kodwa uba isandla sawo singafinyeleli emajubeni amabili loba emaphuphini enkwilimba amabili, lowo owonileyo angaletha umnikelo wakhe okwetshumi \w kwe-efa\w** yempuphu ecolekileyo ube ngumnikelo wesono; angabeki mafutha phezu kwayo, angabeki nhlaka phezu kwayo, ngoba ingumnikelo wesono\x + Nani 5.15.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo uzayiletha kumpristi, umpristi acuphe-ke kuyo isandla sakhe esigcweleyo\x + 2.2.\x* \add kube\add* yisikhumbuzo sayo, akutshise elathini, phezu kweminikelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyenziwe ngomlilo; kungumnikelo wesono\x + 4.35; 1.9.\x*.
\v 13 Ngalokho umpristi uzamenzela inhlawulo yokuthula\x + 4.20,26,31,35; 5.10,16.\x* ngesono sakhe asonileyo lakuyiphi yalezizinto, njalo uzathethelelwa. Njalo kuzakuba ngokompristi\x + 2.3.\x*, njengomnikelo wokudla.
\s Iminikelo yecala
\p
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 15 Uba umphefumulo uphambeka ngesiphambeko wone ungazi umelana lezinto ezingcwele zeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 22.14. Ezra 10.2.\x*, uzaletha umnikelo wawo wecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, inqama engelasici emhlanjini\x + Ezra 10.19.\x*, elesilinganiso sakho sentengo \w samashekeli\w** esiliva ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele, kube ngumnikelo wecala\x + Eks. 38.24.\x*.
\v 16 Lalokho okonileyo okumelene lento engcwele uzakubuyisela, wengezelele kukho ingxenye yesihlanu yakho, oyinike umpristi\x + 6.5; 22.14; 27.13,15,27,31.\x*, lompristi awenzele inhlawulo yokuthula ngenqama yomnikelo wecala, njalo uzathethelelwa\x + 4.26.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Uba-ke umphefumulo usona, wenze \add okumelene\add* lomunye wayo yonke imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 4.2.\x*, okungafanele ukwenziwa, lanxa ungakwazi\x + 5.15; 4.2,13,22,27.\x*, kube kanti ulecala\x + Luka 12.48.\x*, njalo uzathwala ububi bawo.
\v 18 Uzaletha-ke kumpristi inqama engelasici evela emhlanjini\x + 5.15.\x*, elesilinganiso sakho sentengo, kube ngumnikelo wecala, lompristi uzawenzela inhlawulo yokuthula ngokuphambanisa kwawo ophambanisa ngakho ungakwazi, njalo uzathethelelwa\x + 4.26.\x*.
\v 19 Kungumnikelo wecala; ngeqiniso ulecala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.